hgahe+Azad+Eslami|title=URAP - University Ranking by Academic Performance|publisher=|accessdate=16 July 2015}}</ref>\n\n===[[Islamic World Science Citation Database|ISC]] rankings===\n<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.khabaronline.ir/detail/119311/|title=\u0646\u062e\u0633\u062a\u06cc\u0646 \u0631\u062a\u0628\u0647\u200c\u0628\u0646\u062f\u06cc \u0631\u0633\u0645\u06cc \u062f\u0627\u0646\u0634\u06af\u0627\u0647\u200c\u0647\u0627 \u0648 \u0645\u0631\u0627\u06a9\u0632 \u062a\u062d\u0642\u06cc\u0642\u0627\u062a\u06cc \u06a9\u0634\u0648\u0631 \u0627\u0639\u0644\u0627\u0645 \u0634\u062f|publisher=|accessdate=16 July 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ur.isc.gov.ir|title=\u0631\u062a\u0628\u0647 \u0628\u0646\u062f\u06cc \u062f\u0627\u0646\u0634\u06af\u0627\u0647 \u0647\u0627 \u0648 \u0645\u0648\u0633\u0633\u0627\u062a \u067e\u0698\u0648\u0647\u0634\u06cc \u0627\u06cc\u0631\u0627\u0646 \u0648 \u06a9\u0634\u0648\u0631\u0647\u0627\u06cc \u0627\u0633\u0644\u0627\u0645\u06cc|author=|date=|work=isc.gov.ir|accessdate=28 December 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161124234042/http://ur.isc.gov.ir/|archive-date=24 November 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ur.isc.gov.ir/default.aspx?Lan=en|title=Ranking of Iran Universities and Research Institution|work=isc.gov.ir|accessdate=28 December 2016|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223005025/http://ur.isc.gov.ir/default.aspx?Lan=en|archivedate=23 December 2016}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:left;\"\n|+ '''Top 10 branches of the Islamic Azad University in 2010'''\n!Rank\n!Branch\n!Score\n|-\n|1\n|[[Islamic Azad University of Tabriz|Tabriz]]\n|4.27\n|-\n|2\n|[[Islamic Azad University of Mashhad|Mashhad]]\n|3.51\n|-\n|3\n|[[Islamic Azad University Central Tehran Branch|Central Tehran]]\n|3.06\n|-\n|4\n|[[Islamic Azad University of Karaj|Karaj]]\n|2.61\n|-\n|5\n|[[Islamic Azad University North Tehran Branch|North Tehran]]\n|2.48\n|-\n|6\n|[[IAUN|Najafabad]]\n|1.